reagent-name-space-salt = space salt
reagent-desc-space-salt = An opaque solution found in some ore veins of deep-space asteroids. Primarily composed of a rare salt unique to the ore, this sees use in strong analgesic drugs.

reagent-name-klovnide = klovnide
reagent-desc-klovnide = A painkiller mixture based on space salt that allows humanoids to be of sound mind a little bit longer before they go into critical condition. This ups the threshold of damage a humanoid may take before going critical, by 100, and the threshold for death up by 200. Reacts very explosively with plasma.

reagent-name-wittel = Wittel
reagent-desc-wittel = Only found as a product of geysers. Does nothing by itself.

reagent-name-gravitum = gravitum
reagent-desc-gravitum = Makes living beings completely weightless as long as it's in their system.
